title: #92Noon!  10am Hour 8/15 - Vikes Calls, Creative Coachses, KOC Post-Game Presser
description: PA takes your calls on everything Vikings/Raiders, discusses how Kliff Kingsbury & Andy Reid are keeping players excited, plus a listen back to Vikings Head Coach Kevin O'Connell's post-game presser following the Vikings loss to the Raiders.
